headline: Top 3 Large-Cap US Auto Stocks to Steer Your Portfolio in 2025
summary: As the U.S. auto industry navigates an uncertain landscape in 2025, large-cap stocks like TSLA, GM and KMX offer a balanced blend of stability and growth potential.

headline: Why Fast-paced Mover CarMax (KMX) Is a Great Choice for Value Investors
summary: If you are looking for stocks that have gained strong momentum recently but are still trading at reasonable prices, CarMax (KMX) could be a great choice. It is one of the several stocks that passed through our 'Fast-Paced Momentum at a Bargain' screen.
